@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 60
skinparam ranksep 55

title Diagram komponentów i wdrożenia - CryptoTrack

node "Przeglądarka użytkownika" as Browser {
  component "Aplikacja web\nNext.js 15 / React 19\napps/web" as Web
  component "Rozszerzenie Chrome\nPlasmo MV3\napps/extension" as Extension
}

cloud "MetaMask Card\ncard.metamask.io\nportfolio.metamask.io" as MetaMask

node "Serwer aplikacji" as AppServer {
  component "API REST\nNestJS + Fastify\napps/api" as Api
  component "Auth Module\nJWT + SIWE" as Auth
  component "Transactions Module" as Transactions
  component "Categories Module" as Categories
  component "CardTransactions Module" as CardTx
  component "OpenAI Categorization\nService" as OpenAIService
}

database "PostgreSQL" as Db
component "Prisma ORM\npackages/db" as Prisma
component "@crypto-tracker/shared\nschemas + types" as Shared
cloud "OpenAI API" as OpenAI

Web -right-> Api : HTTPS REST\nJWT Bearer
Extension -right-> Api : HTTPS REST\nExtension token
Extension -down-> MetaMask : DOM scraping

Auth -[hidden]down- Transactions
Transactions -[hidden]down- Categories
Categories -[hidden]down- CardTx

Api -down-> Auth
Api -down-> Transactions
Api -down-> Categories
Api -down-> CardTx
Transactions -right-> Prisma
Categories -right-> Prisma
CardTx -right-> Prisma
Prisma -right-> Db : SQL

Api .down.> Shared : shared DTO/types
Transactions -down-> OpenAIService : AI categorization
OpenAIService -right-> OpenAI : HTTPS

note bottom
  Wdrożenie lokalne/projektowe:
  pnpm + Turbo, Docker / Docker Compose,
  PostgreSQL jako główna baza danych.
end note

@enduml
